data.description: Tesoro Club is a 1,400-acre gated master planned community located on Florida’s Treasure Coast. The community is home to a wide variety of luxury single family homes overlooking the lakes and fairways of two championship golf courses. Tesoro Club is also home to the Crane Club, a premiere wedding and event venue managed by the renowned Lessing’s Hospitality Group. The magnificent Clubhouse boasts over 100,000 square feet, with the ability to accommodate up to 250 guests for dining and reception services. This idyllic location can host a myriad of events, ranging from grand proceedings to small intimate gatherings, while tailoring the ambiance to meet each client’s specific needs and tastes.
